Beverly Aadland https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Beverly_Aadland 0 Beverly Elaine Aadland (September 16, 1942 – January 5, 2010) was an American film actress. She appeared in films including South Pacific. As a teenager, she co-starred in the Errol Flynn film Cuban Rebel Girls, and later entered a relationship with him.
